{"tid":1672840,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"面具","createTime":"2019-10-24T10:23:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-24T10:23:40.000Z","uid":140655,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"3a0309d71ec2a9a7f3464a285b91b44d702dcafc","tid":1672840,"uid":140655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T10:23:40.000Z","msg":"許廷鏗 <br />\n<br />\n面具<br />\n<br />\n作詞：許廷鏗．劉卓輝<br />\n作曲：彭學斌<br />\n編曲：韋景雲<br />\n監製：韋景雲<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">發過要發的夢</span></span></strong>　但熱烈漸覺冰凍<br />\n跌過痛過便會懂<br />\n誰在作弄　沉默背後也想發狂<br />\n很想找一剎來放縱　<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">斗膽一次如反恐</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n◎也試過太衝動　大件事沒計輕重<br />\n　<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>錯過悔過仍要衝</strong></span></span><br />\n　衝出困局　形象似義勇軍般英勇<br />\n　但結果有沒有停戰的溝通<br />\n<br />\n※如戴著面具去掩飾倦容<br />\n　<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>迎著炮火也依然表情輕鬆</strong></span></span><br />\n　情緒不可激動　還若輕的舉重<br />\n　來化解一切壓力似失蹤<br />\n　如放下面具去也許面紅<br />\n　乘著晚風去追尋逍遙星空<br />\n　除去假的寬容　還真想不通<br />\n　曾年少的青蔥　<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">懷着理想哪怕痛</span></span></strong>(忘卻世間的縳束)<br />\n<br />\n＊<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>誰明白像和你也許重逢</strong></span></span><br />\n　遺憾太多卻不能倒流的鐘<br />\n　如琴聲的哀號　連結他都哭訴<br />\n　誰明白我初衷　煩躁也是個夢　但我真的痛<br />\n<br />\nrepeat ◎, (※), ＊<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/yrnKlUS-blg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FyrnKlUS-blg&d=pzn6Hq8jxzH2PmSSbZvUofaDgzkAO6tKN2FhpyhCcE0%3D&h=2e33f4e9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/yrnKlUS-blg</a>"}]}